        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1785341671" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5146990765113640239">Marcel Proust is a writer I completely miss the point of. I have no interest in society, especially this dead French one. I can&apos;t seem to interest myself in these children&apos;s parties or these petite bourgeois parents scheming to meet this or that VIP government minister. My God, the tedium! Yet Tolstoy and Bellow and Ozick and scores of others have all written about particular dead cultures which I&apos;ve enjoyed reading about immensely. I can&apos;t put my finger on it with Proust. His inability to invol</span>
  <span id="freeText5146990765113640239" style="display:none">Marcel Proust is a writer I completely miss the point of. I have no interest in society, especially this dead French one. I can't seem to interest myself in these children's parties or these petite bourgeois parents scheming to meet this or that VIP government minister. My God, the tedium! Yet Tolstoy and Bellow and Ozick and scores of others have all written about particular dead cultures which I've enjoyed reading about immensely. I can't put my finger on it with Proust. His inability to involve me remains a mystery. Well, I shall stop trying to read him and cut my losses for good.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5146990765113640239" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

